a project that splits weekly addresses by obama into word segments and stores them in a psql db with meta data. as well as an app for compiling said data into video files again


relies on prosodylab.aligner and aligner models/eng dicts are form their repo


Please you use this tool; we would appreciate if you cited the following paper:

Gorman, Kyle, Jonathan Howell and Michael Wagner. 2011. Prosodylab-Aligner: A Tool for Forced Alignment of Laboratory Speech. Canadian Acoustics. 39.3. 192â€“193.
